You find all documentation for problectix in:

/usr/share/texmf/doc/latex/problectix

Installation von problectix unter debian
============================================================

1. Add the line to /etc/apt/sources.list:

   deb http://cvs.bszleo.de/problectix/debs .

2. apt-get install problectix-teacher-texlive

3. If you use emacs, do:

   apt-get install problectix-teacher-texlive-emacs


Pur you collection of problems into the following directoty_

   $HOME/cvs/mytex

rr edit /etc/environment to change $TEXINPUTS




